Package: comrad
Type: Package
Title: R implementation of a Competitive Radiation model
Version: 2.2.1
Description: Simulation of communities with an individual-based model with
  Lotka-Volterra competition, and study of the form of diversity-dependent 
  diversification that emerges from it.
